{
  "id": "69d10a8ecc41871a7ea92932",
  "title": "共同日記が読みづらい",
  "created": 1775307409,
  "updated": 1775307778,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d10a8ecc41871a7ea92932",
      "text": "共同日記が読みづらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307409,
      "updated": 1775307409
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10a900000000000d7d091",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307409,
      "updated": 1775307409
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10a910000000000d7d093",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307410,
      "updated": 1775307424
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10a9f0000000000d7d094",
      "text": "\t最近思ったことだけど、[共同日記]が読みづらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307424,
      "updated": 1775307434
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b960000000000d7d0a1",
      "text": "\t\t読みやすく工夫できるのは[infobox日記]の利点だと思った",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307671,
      "updated": 1775307778
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10aaa0000000000d7d095",
      "text": "\t思い当たる理由",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307434,
      "updated": 1775307447
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10ab20000000000d7d096",
      "text": "\t\t重い。読み込みだけでもとにかく重い。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307442,
      "updated": 1775307472
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10acd0000000000d7d097",
      "text": "\t\t\t[intel入ってる]PCであってもページ読み込みに数秒かかる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307470,
      "updated": 1775307514
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10afa0000000000d7d098",
      "text": "\t\t\t画像読み込みも含めるともっとかかる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307515,
      "updated": 1775307536
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b040000000000d7d09a",
      "text": "\t\t長い。縦にとにかく長い。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307525,
      "updated": 1775307555
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b1d0000000000d7d09b",
      "text": "\t\t\t更新探すのに毎回[高速スクロール]してる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307549,
      "updated": 1775307587
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b450000000000d7d09c",
      "text": "\t\t\t上の方の文章は２回目以降は大体読んでるのでもう読む必要がない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307590,
      "updated": 1775307610
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b5a0000000000d7d09d",
      "text": "\t\t文章が読む人向けに書かれていない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307610,
      "updated": 1775307626
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b610000000000d7d09e",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれは日記なので仕方ない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307618,
      "updated": 1775307629
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b6d0000000000d7d09f",
      "text": "\t\tレイアウトが読みやすいものではない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307629,
      "updated": 1775307641
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10b790000000000d7d0a0",
      "text": "\t\t\t[きまぐれ]が起きない限り、基本的にはアイコンを上に置いてその下に箇条書きで個人のトピックを書くだけ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307641,
      "updated": 1775307706
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10bba0000000000d7d0a2",
      "text": "\t\t\tトピックごとに空行で分割できないので、視覚的に塊を把握しづらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307707,
      "updated": 1775307759
    },
    {
      "id": "69d10a900000000000d7d092",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775307409,
      "updated": 1775307409
    }
  ]
}